<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Confirm-email</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="../css-hbs/confirm-email.css" />
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Montserrat:ital,wght@0,100;0,200;0,300;0,400;0,500;0,600;0,700;0,800;0,900;1,100;1,200;1,300;1,400;1,500;1,600;1,700;1,800;1,900&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        @font-face {
        font-family: "Montserrat";
        src: url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Montserrat:ital,wght@0,100;0,200;0,300;0,400;0,500;0,600;0,700;0,800;0,900;1,100;1,200;1,300;1,400;1,500;1,600;1,700;1,800;1,900&display=swap');
        }
        #container {
            width: 100%;
            height: 95vh;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
        }
        #container *{
            text-decoration: none;
            font-family: 'montserrat';
        }
        
        #content {
            background-color: lightgrey;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 10px 50px;
            border-radius: 20px;
        }
        
        #confirm-email-button {
            width: 150px;
            height: 50px;
            cursor: pointer;
            background-color: rgb(89, 175, 236);
            border-radius: 10px;
            border: 0;
        }
        #confirm-email-button:hover{
            transition-duration: 0.5s;
            background-color: rgb(36, 131, 199);
        }
        #confirm-email-button > a{
            font-size: 20px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: white !important;
        }

        #user-status-color::after{
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            margin-left: 10px;
            margin-top: 15px;
            width: 10px;
            height: 10px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            background-color: rgb(76, 209, 0);
        }
        
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <div id="container">
        <div id="content">
            <h1>Olá {{{name}}},</h1>
            {{#if status }}
            <h1 id="user-status-color" >{{{msg}}}</h1>
            <p>Clique botão abaixo para acessar sua conta</p>
            <button id="confirm-email-button"><a href="{{{url_font}}}">OK</a></button>
            <p>Ou copie esta url e cole na barra de pesquisa do seu navegador</p>
            <p>http://localhost:3000/login</p>
        {{else }}
            <p>{{{msg}}} </p> 
            <p>Tente novamente ou contate o suporte</p>
        {{/if }}
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>